935
00:37:03,500 --> 00:37:04,740
 da su ljudi mogli čuti

936
00:37:04,740 --> 00:37:07,640
 zbog akustike osobu,

937
00:37:07,640 --> 00:37:08,740
 da je tri i po tisući ljudi

938
00:37:08,740 --> 00:37:09,680
 mogli čuti jednu osobu

939
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:10,380
 od prilike.

940
00:37:10,460 --> 00:37:13,080
 Ali ono što je isto bitno

941
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:13,640
 zaznati

942
00:37:13,640 --> 00:37:15,420
 i kako kažeš da,

943
00:37:15,420 --> 00:37:16,060
 recimo,

944
00:37:16,060 --> 00:37:18,040
 u novije doba je poznatije

945
00:37:18,040 --> 00:37:19,360
 ta popularnost

946
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,180
 na način na koju oduživljamo danas,

947
00:37:21,180 --> 00:37:23,960
 ali i u to doba je postalo

948
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:26,440
 prenošenje od čovjeka do čovjeka,

949
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:28,320
 riječ ide od čovjeka

950
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,020
 prema čovjeku,

951
00:37:29,020 --> 00:37:31,040
 preko pojedinaca.

952
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:36,820
 i s obzirom na tu zapisanu povijest

953
00:37:36,820 --> 00:37:40,140
 koju imamo od prilike 5000 godina,

954
00:37:40,140 --> 00:37:43,240
 da pokušamo promatrati neutralno.

955
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:48,340
 da li ti smatraš da je osoba,

956
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:50,180
 kao što je Isus Hrist,

957
00:37:50,180 --> 00:37:53,400
 postojala prema zapisanoj povijesti?

958
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:56,880
 To je sad pitanje za milijun dolara

959
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:59,560
 i mislim da ono to nije pitanje

960
00:37:59,560 --> 00:38:03,340
 znati, nego to je pitanje vjerovati.

961
00:38:04,340 --> 00:38:06,020
 Ali što povijest kaže?

962
00:38:06,020 --> 00:38:07,920
 Ako postoji zapisa na povijest?

963
00:38:07,920 --> 00:38:09,120
 Povijest sad ovako,

964
00:38:09,120 --> 00:38:10,000
 dakle postoje,

965
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:12,740
 ovisi ko ga pitate,

966
00:38:12,740 --> 00:38:14,260
 ali recimo da je nekakav,

967
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:15,440
 neću reći konsenzus,

968
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,940
 zapravo nije to pitanje konsenzusa,

969
00:38:16,940 --> 00:38:19,700
 dakle u istinu smatra se da je

970
00:38:19,700 --> 00:38:23,840
 u istinu se pojavio negdje tamo

971
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,760
 u to jedno vrijeme

972
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:29,620
 na prelazu ovoga iz Novog,

973
00:38:29,620 --> 00:38:32,220
 mi te kažemo prije Krista,

974
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,640
 poslije Kristal zapravo ima onaj naziv

975
00:38:34,640 --> 00:38:36,560
 prije Nove ere i ovoga,

976
00:38:36,560 --> 00:38:38,340
 poslije Nove ere,

977
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:40,320
 dakle da je u istinu,

978
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:44,120
 ja pretpostavljam da je vrlo lako moguće

979
00:38:44,120 --> 00:38:45,660
 ta osoba bila tamo,

980
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:48,120
 jer ne bi nastalo sve to što je nastalo,

981
00:38:48,120 --> 00:38:50,160
 dakle s ono što mi znamo kao Novi Zavijet

982
00:38:50,160 --> 00:38:52,160
 i ono što znamo kao i one,

983
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:53,880
 oni dijelovi,

984
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:56,440
 oni tekstovi koji nisu ušli u Novi Zavijet,

985
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:59,480
 dakle Novi Zavijet je samo jedan manji paket,

986
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:01,400
 puno je toga više napisano,

987
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:03,820
 samo jednostavno nije ušlo ono što bi se nazvalo kanon.

988
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:06,100
 Postoje neki zapisi

989
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:10,320
 koji bi zapravo dali nas lutiti da je u istinu

990
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,500
 postao

991
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:14,740
 Isusa recimo kod Josipa Flavija,

992
00:39:14,740 --> 00:39:17,600
 tog zapravo židovskog povisničara

993
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:20,080
 koji je za vrijeme židovskog ustaka

994
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:24,000
 se zapravo de facto romanizirao recimo to tako,

995
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,260
 jer su rimljani pobjedili,

996
00:39:25,260 --> 00:39:27,380
 nije baš nimao ni pretjerano izbor.

997
00:39:28,380 --> 00:39:29,340
 Ali opet,

998
00:39:29,340 --> 00:39:32,280
 to može biti dokaz

999
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:34,240
 da on u istinu postoje.

1000
00:39:34,240 --> 00:39:37,120
 Pravo pitanje je

1001
00:39:37,120 --> 00:39:39,820
 kakav je on bio,

1002
00:39:39,820 --> 00:39:42,020
 to mi znamo ako vjerujemo

1003
00:39:42,020 --> 00:39:43,600
 u Novi Zavijet.

1004
00:39:44,600 --> 00:39:47,340
 Ako nam opet Novi Zavijet je samo nekakva vrsta

1005
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:48,540
 povijesnog izvora,

1006
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:51,640
 moguće da bi bio posve drugačiji,

1007
00:39:51,640 --> 00:39:53,700
 jer rekao sve one riječi koje je rekao.

1008
00:39:55,160 --> 00:39:56,340
 To je sad veliko pitanje.

1009
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:57,760
 S obzirom da je vriječ o

1010
00:39:57,760 --> 00:40:00,200
 sinu Božjem,

1011
00:40:00,200 --> 00:40:00,700
 ako ćemo,

1012
00:40:00,700 --> 00:40:02,500
 pari se tako govori,

1013
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:05,940
 onda u tom mislim da tu više nije pitanje,

1014
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:07,240
 čak ni toliko povijesti.

1015
00:40:07,240 --> 00:40:09,200
 To je pitanje vjerovanja.

1016
00:40:09,200 --> 00:40:10,080
 Ključno pitanje je

1017
00:40:10,080 --> 00:40:11,720
 vjerujete li vi da je on bio ili nije?

1018
00:40:11,720 --> 00:40:13,520
 To je li on bio ili ne?

1019
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:14,220
 Krajnjoj liniji,

1020
00:40:14,220 --> 00:40:16,900
 čak mislim da nije ni toliko bitno.

1021
00:40:17,740 --> 00:40:18,420
 zato što

1022
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:21,180
 čak recimo da vi kažete

1023
00:40:21,180 --> 00:40:21,900
 nije postao.

1024
00:40:21,900 --> 00:40:24,620
 Šta to znači ljudima koji vjeruju da je postao?

1025
00:40:24,620 --> 00:40:25,000
 Ništa.

1026
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,680
 Mislim da postoji velika razlika

1027
00:40:26,680 --> 00:40:29,020
 između toga da potvrdiš da je neko postao

1028
00:40:29,020 --> 00:40:31,680
 u odnosu na to da je on sin Božji.

1029
00:40:31,680 --> 00:40:33,180
 Naravno, kažem,

1030
00:40:33,180 --> 00:40:34,540
 oma je stvar vjerovanja

1031
00:40:34,540 --> 00:40:36,680
 i kad je u pitanju vjerovanja

1032
00:40:36,680 --> 00:40:40,940
 to je jedan posve drugačiji paket i pristup.

1033
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:41,900
 Dakle, tu nema,

1034
00:40:41,900 --> 00:40:44,000
 u vjerovanju nema dokaza.

1035
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:45,740
 Vi vjerujete ili ne vjerujete.

1036
00:40:45,860 --> 00:40:48,020
 Ako morate dokazivati ni u pitanju vjera.

1037
00:40:48,020 --> 00:40:50,480
 To je ključ cijele priče.

1038
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:52,160
 Tako i kažem, sa Isusom Kristom

1039
00:40:52,160 --> 00:40:54,260
 definitivno, kako da kažem,

1040
00:40:54,260 --> 00:40:57,280
 ne bi bilo svega onoga što se dogodilo.

1041
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:59,440
 Da je on izmišljena osoba.

1042
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:02,400
 Jer jednostavno, previše je toga,

1043
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:04,700
 previše se toga dogodilo.

1044
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:05,320
 E sad,

1045
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:08,160
 je li Isus Krist,

1046
00:41:08,160 --> 00:41:11,380
 onaj kojeg mi sad znamo

1047
00:41:11,380 --> 00:41:12,860
 iz Pravije iz Novog Zavijeta,

1048
00:41:12,860 --> 00:41:14,480
 jednak onome koji je bio

1049
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,580
 ili je u pitanju,

1050
00:41:15,580 --> 00:41:19,640
 to je sad pitanje na koje isto se pokušava odgovorit

1051
00:41:19,640 --> 00:41:20,660
 o ho-ho godina.

1052
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:21,240
 Kažem,

1053
00:41:21,240 --> 00:41:24,340
 ali na kraju se sve svodi u pitanje vjerovanja.

1054
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:26,160
 Vi imate

1055
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:28,540
 niz knjiga koji su napisane,

1056
00:41:28,540 --> 00:41:30,480
 koji su pokušavale odgovorit

1057
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:32,060
 kako je to moguće bilo,

1058
00:41:32,060 --> 00:41:32,940
 kako je krenula

1059
00:41:32,940 --> 00:41:34,140
 zapravo ta

1060
00:41:34,140 --> 00:41:38,340
 nova sljedba unutar židovstva.

1061
00:41:38,340 --> 00:41:40,040
 Dakle, Isus je bio židov.

1062
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:42,040
 Dakle, to su sve židovi oko njega.

1063
00:41:42,040 --> 00:41:43,200
 Apostoli su židovi.

1064
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:47,880
 ali ta nova vjera koja dolazi,

1065
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:52,480
 koja je sad rasprava koja će se voditi o ho-ho?

1066
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:53,240
 Mislim,

1067
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:56,800
 tu nema po meni nekakvog odgovora

1068
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:59,640
 koji bi bio definitivno povisničarski.

1069
00:42:00,180 --> 00:42:01,340
 Jer u tom slučaju,

1070
00:42:01,340 --> 00:42:01,680
 kažem,

1071
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,560
 čak ni to,

1072
00:42:02,560 --> 00:42:04,620
 ja sam sklon tvrditi da,

1073
00:42:04,620 --> 00:42:06,420
 vjerujem da je u istinu se to,

1074
00:42:06,420 --> 00:42:07,880
 da je postoje,

1075
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:09,900
 ali ne bi se dogodilo sve ovo.

1076
00:42:09,900 --> 00:42:11,700
 A sad ovaj dio,

1077
00:42:11,700 --> 00:42:13,140
 sin Boži,

1078
00:42:13,140 --> 00:42:15,380
 sve to trojstvo,

1079
00:42:15,380 --> 00:42:15,720
 čuda.

1080
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:17,360
 To je pitanje vjere.

1081
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:19,120
 To već nije pitanje dokaza.

1082
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:21,940
 To da li je se nešto dogodilo,

1083
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:26,620
 to već isključivo ima veze sa vjerom,

1084
00:42:26,620 --> 00:42:28,700
 a teško da ima veze sa dokazom,

1085
00:42:28,700 --> 00:42:29,420
 jer, kažem,

1086
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:32,300
 tu čak i pitanje dokaza nije ni relevantno.

1087
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:34,820
 To je jednostavno izašlo izvan povijesti

1088
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:35,800
 i postalo vjera.

1089
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:38,460
 Što je to odmah na jednoj drugoj razini,

1090
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:39,000
 kažem?

1091
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:42,760
 Je, čini mi se recimo Mahatma Gandhi

1092
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:45,300
 koji je živio u nedavnoj povijesti,

1093
00:42:45,300 --> 00:42:49,720
 za njega možemo reći da je živio,

1094
00:42:49,720 --> 00:42:51,680
 da je bio živa osoba,

1095
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:53,980
 i postoje neki dokaze.

1096
00:42:53,980 --> 00:42:56,020
 Mislim, danas uz ovu umjetnu inteligenciju

1097
00:42:56,020 --> 00:42:57,520
 i sve te stvari koje se događuje,

1098
00:42:58,320 --> 00:42:59,300
 sve je teže i teže,

1099
00:42:59,300 --> 00:43:01,940
 razaznati šta je istina, šta nije,

1100
00:43:01,940 --> 00:43:02,860
 šta je realno, šta nije,

1101
00:43:02,860 --> 00:43:04,420
 ali ne ulazimo sad u tu duboku filozofiju.

1102
00:43:04,420 --> 00:43:06,380
 Kad je tu pitanje, opet kažem,

1103
00:43:06,380 --> 00:43:07,600
 to je jedan paket,

1104
00:43:07,600 --> 00:43:09,340
 kad uđe vjera u sve,

1105
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:11,200
 onda su stvari drugačije.

1106
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:12,720
 Misliš religija zapravo?

1107
00:43:12,720 --> 00:43:13,240
 Tako je, da.

1108
00:43:13,240 --> 00:43:17,540
 To je ona jedna sjajna scena iz filma,

1109
00:43:17,540 --> 00:43:21,900
 mislim, krvavjerik, da, od Monty Pythona,

1110
00:43:21,900 --> 00:43:24,900
 kad zapravo oni idu prema Valhali,

1111
00:43:24,900 --> 00:43:25,660
 oni su vikinzi,

1112
00:43:25,660 --> 00:43:27,260
 oni idu prema Valhali,

1113
00:43:27,260 --> 00:43:28,700
 i s njima je jedan redovnik,

1114
00:43:28,700 --> 00:43:30,280
 koji ih pokušava bezuspješno

1115
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:33,760
 na kršćanstvo preobratiti,

1116
00:43:34,300 --> 00:43:35,660
 i sad uglavnom u jednom trenutku

1117
00:43:35,660 --> 00:43:36,540
 oni plove, plove,

1118
00:43:36,540 --> 00:43:38,740
 i svi vikinzi vide ispred sebe Valhalu

1119
00:43:38,740 --> 00:43:41,860
 sa dvo vratima ogromnim

1120
00:43:41,860 --> 00:43:43,500
 i sad svi viču Valhala,

1121
00:43:43,500 --> 00:43:44,940
 jedino taj redovnik gleda i kaže

1122
00:43:44,940 --> 00:43:46,580
 što vi vidite, ja ne vidim ništa.

1123
00:43:46,580 --> 00:43:48,980
 To je to pitanje.

1124
00:43:48,980 --> 00:43:50,140
 To su dvije rezine.

1125
00:43:50,140 --> 00:43:52,840
 Dakle, jedni vjeruju u to da postoji Valhala

1126
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:55,680
 i da unutra ratnici se tuku

1127
00:43:55,680 --> 00:43:56,640
 od jutra do mraka,

1128
00:43:56,640 --> 00:43:59,580
 piju medovinu i uživaju u svom životu,

1129
00:43:59,580 --> 00:44:01,120
 drugi misle da ne vidi ništa,

1130
00:44:01,120 --> 00:44:01,940
 vidi samo more.

1131
00:44:01,940 --> 00:44:03,680
 Tako je ovdje.

1132
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:05,640
 Vjera, religija,

1133
00:44:05,640 --> 00:44:08,460
 tiže stvari na jednu drugu razinu.

1134
00:44:08,460 --> 00:44:10,360
 Ovo je, mi možemo raspravljati

1135
00:44:10,360 --> 00:44:12,120
 o rimskom carstvu na prilazu

1136
00:44:12,120 --> 00:44:13,280
 i stare u novo eru,

1137
00:44:13,280 --> 00:44:14,940
 mi možemo razgovarati o tome

1138
00:44:14,940 --> 00:44:16,860
 zašto je Poncije Pilat

1139
00:44:16,860 --> 00:44:18,880
 dopremio munjevitu legiju

1140
00:44:18,880 --> 00:44:19,600
 i tako dalje,

1141
00:44:19,600 --> 00:44:20,720
 koji su bili neredi

1142
00:44:20,720 --> 00:44:22,900
 i vjerojatno u tom neredu

1143
00:44:22,900 --> 00:44:24,580
 ona priča o tome

1144
00:44:24,580 --> 00:44:26,060
 da su se rimljeni bojali nereda,

1145
00:44:26,060 --> 00:44:27,840
 a onda i nakon toga je židavska zajednica

1146
00:44:27,840 --> 00:44:30,120
 što će rimljeni napraviti zbog tog nereda.

1147
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:31,200
 Sve to vjerojatno stoji

1148
00:44:31,200 --> 00:44:32,020
 i to je napravljeno.

1149
00:44:32,020 --> 00:44:32,940
 Ali ovaj dio

1150
00:44:32,940 --> 00:44:36,060
 Isus Krist, kojeg mi znamo,

1151
00:44:36,060 --> 00:44:37,560
 to više nije stvar povijesti.

1152
00:44:37,560 --> 00:44:39,500
 To jednostavno izlazi iz

1153
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:42,200
 povijesne rasprave

1154
00:44:42,200 --> 00:44:43,280
 i postoje dio vjere.

1155
00:44:43,280 --> 00:44:44,780
 To je već drugi paket.

1156
00:44:44,780 --> 00:44:47,780
 Jedna od fascinantnijih knjiga

1157
00:44:47,780 --> 00:44:48,920
 koju sam pročitao

1158
00:44:48,920 --> 00:44:51,160
 u toj kategoriji povijesti

1159
00:44:51,160 --> 00:44:53,260
 mi je

1160
00:44:53,260 --> 00:44:54,980
 Lessons of History,

1161
00:44:54,980 --> 00:44:56,460
 lekcije povijesti,

1162
00:44:56,460 --> 00:44:59,740
 autori Will i Ariel Durant.

1163
00:44:59,740 --> 00:45:01,020
 jeste čuli za njih,

1164
00:45:01,020 --> 00:45:01,680
 ste čitali to.

1165
00:45:01,680 --> 00:45:02,720
 Čuo sam za njih,

1166
00:45:02,720 --> 00:45:03,640
 ali nisam čital.

1167
00:45:03,640 --> 00:45:05,300
 Fascinantna knjiga.

1168
00:45:05,300 --> 00:45:08,620
 Jedan od razloga zašto je meni fascinantna,

1169
00:45:08,620 --> 00:45:11,060
 zato što opisuje povijest

1170
00:45:11,060 --> 00:45:13,860
 promatrajući je kroz različite

1171
00:45:13,860 --> 00:45:15,440
 perspektive.

1172
00:45:15,440 --> 00:45:17,440
 Religija i povijest,

1173
00:45:17,440 --> 00:45:18,880
 politika i povijest,

1174
00:45:18,880 --> 00:45:20,140
 ekonomija i povijest.

1175
00:45:20,860 --> 00:45:21,660
 I to je zapravo

1176
00:45:21,660 --> 00:45:24,140
 u toj knjizi je sumirano

1177
00:45:24,140 --> 00:45:26,260
 dvanajstak volumena

1178
00:45:26,260 --> 00:45:28,440
 tih razno raznih

